Styled.title: Image Stylization
Styled.desc: Upload a portrait photo and you can start a magical transformation
Styled.usage-title: Usage: You can try the following methods
Styled.usage1: Switch to 「demo」 in the bottom left corner, select 「style」, and then click 「start」;
Styled.usage2: Enter an online image address directly in the 「Link」, select 「style」, and then click 「start」;
Styled.usage3: Click 「Upload」 in the bottom left corner, select 「Style」, and then click 「Start」
